

  s/w appln
  --------------------
  
  
     a. application ==> process
     b. datasource  ==> persist
     
     
     A. application
     
         - Object Model
         
     B. datasource
     
     	   - file-system	
     
     	   - RDBMS products ( SQL based )
     	   
     	   		=> Relational/Entity Model
     	   
     	   - NoSQL ( e.g MongoDB ) 
     	   
 ----------------------------------------------------
 
 
 
 bookshop
 
 	Publisher => id,name
 
 	Book      => isbn,name,price,author  
 	
 	Chapters  => (idx,isbn) , title
 	
----------------------------------------------------------


    publisher  ===> book     ==>  chapter
 	
